name: Experiment Or Die #3
description: We've all done some foolish things in our lives and hopefully at the very least we all learned something from those mistakes. In what seems like another life now I got to spend a few days in Fulton County Jail. What did I learn?? I never want to go back. That event marked the end of a low period in my life...it was the bottom. From there, there was nowhere to go but up. IG: Nikejerk
